data.description: Beautifully renovated 3 bedrooms 2 bathroom home features a bonus room that can be used as an office or a 4th bedroom. Upgraded kitchen with granite counter-tops and stainless steel appliances. Fenced in yard with plenty of space for entertaining. One car garage with extra space for tools and a work bench. Conveniently located near beaches, bases, restaurants , shopping and more.  Assumable VA Loan for first time home buyers.
